data.description: AGGRESSIVELY PRICED! Owners Motivated. Home needs some tlc for instant equity. Main has open floor plan with hardwood throughout. Great for entertaining. Kitchen features: granite countertops w/ample bar eating space and nice size pantry. Primary bedroom has bonus room. Perfect for nursery, craft area, or home office, a extra-large walk-in closet, and 5-piece primary bath. Additional full bath and utility room conveniently located adjacent to bedrooms. Good size side yard for bbq's
